==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spale
<hw>Spale</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. <er>Spell</er> a
splinter.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A lath; a shaving or chip, as of wood
or stone.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng. & Scot.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Shipbuilding)</fld> <def>A strengthening cross
timber.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spall</ent>⟦br⟧
